# GitHub Linguist 配置
# 用于控制 GitHub 仓库语言统计

# 排除 node_modules 和构建文件（这些不应该计入语言统计）
node_modules/** linguist-vendored
**/node_modules/** linguist-vendored
**/.next/** linguist-vendored
**/dist/** linguist-vendored
**/build/** linguist-vendored

# 排除生成的文件
**/*.pyc linguist-generated
**/__pycache__/** linguist-generated
**/venv/** linguist-vendored
**/env/** linguist-vendored

# 排除数据文件
**/*.json linguist-documentation
**/*.yaml linguist-documentation
**/*.yml linguist-documentation

# 排除字体文件
**/*.ttf linguist-vendored
**/*.otf linguist-vendored

# 排除图片文件
**/*.png linguist-vendored
**/*.jpg linguist-vendored
**/*.jpeg linguist-vendored
**/*.gif linguist-vendored
**/*.svg linguist-vendored

# 排除缓存和临时文件
**/.cache/** linguist-vendored
**/tmp/** linguist-vendored
**/temp/** linguist-vendored

